Why don't you have a go?
Show them what it takes.

segmentosSRT.text: It's all in order, I'll be going.

segmentosSRT.text: Master Fugui, don't think badly of me...
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: But I sure like that mansion of yours.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: See you there in a few days.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: and then set fire to the place.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: And we've painted Chairman Mao's portrait.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: What do you think about Fengxia and me?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Lunch is all taken care of.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Dad, Mom, we're having a baby.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: They say she's great. No problems.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: From the contractions, not right now.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: Go ask where the doctors are.

me and my wife,
saying she wasn't fit to reproduce.

segmentosSRT.text: I was putting on a show.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: I wanted you here for her sake.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_05

segmentosSRT.text: If you get a car from the factory...

segmentosSRT.text: You two get the car, we'll be fine.

segmentosSRT.text:
We should've bought them
on the way home.

segmentosSRT.text: Now we've got to carry them!

I'll do it.
